CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 10, 1962, pg. 20A reads: "Dapper Dollies - Among hostesses at the Dapper Dan banquet were (left to right): Norma Small, Georgia White and Carmen Sabo, who was crowned "Dapper Dan Queen." - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women, some wearing wearing Dapper Dan Charities sashes, including Georgia White seated fourth from left, posed in interior for Dapper Dan banquet, another version
